
                   geant4-00-01-ref-13
                   ===================

geant4-00-01-ref-13 is geant4-00-01-ref-12 plus:

vis-V00-01-10        - Header files for SRM.
config-V00-01-14     - Tidying.
transport-V00-01-01  - transportation.cc: Added protection for the case
                       of a zero step (when there is a field).
                     - UserSpecialCuts: Protection to use min range
                       and min kinE only for charged particles.
global-V00-01-13     - inline STL Interface template member functions again. 
                     - rationalise STLInterface cstring.h.
geomvol-V00-01-01    - G4TouchableHistory: made GetTranslation and
                       GetRotation non-inline.
                     - G4PropagatorInField: Initialised fVerboseLevel
                       in constructor.
